The American Society of Tax Problem Solvers (ASTPS) is a non-profit organization of tax professionals in the United States. The organization offers training and accreditation to tax and legal professionals. Any tax professional can join ASTPS. Full membership, however, is open only for persons licensed as Certified Public Accountants (CPAs), Lawyers, or Enrolled Agents (EAs).
ASTPS directs the Certified Tax Resolution Specialist (CTRS) examination and certification.
